[13/05/2019 20:21:20] <font color="#ffffff">No.</font>
[13/05/2019 20:21:29] <font color="#ffffff">(R EN)</font>
[13/05/2019 20:21:31] <font color="#ffff00">Estamos yendo al McGovern</font>
[13/05/2019 20:21:34] <font color="#ffff00">y al Picower Institute,</font>
[13/05/2019 20:21:34] <font color="#ffff00">de neurociencia,</font>
