[13/05/2019 22:40:33] <font color="#ffff00">(R E)</font>
[13/05/2019 22:40:33] <font color="#ffffff">Dice: "Ay, mísero de mí".</font>
[13/05/2019 22:40:35] <font color="#ffffff">(R EN)</font>
